      The entire text of the Apache License 2.0 is <em>much longer</em> than that of the MIT license. If interested in the details, see <url href="https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html" visual="www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0">Apache License 2.0</url>.
   </p>
